Hey Zoe, don’t know if you will read this as I know you get a load of comments, but some advice for the plants that don’t look so happy: since getting a load of house plants myself I have noticed it makes a massive difference (if you have quite hard water) for certain plants if you use either rain water or filtered water to water the plants.
